import { FormGroup,FormControl,InputLabel,Input,Button } from "@material-ui/core";

const AddUsers = () => {
    return (
        <FormGroup>
            <FormControl>
                <InputLabel>Registration Number</InputLabel>
                <Input />
            </FormControl>
            <FormControl>
                <InputLabel>Name</InputLabel>
                <Input />
            </FormControl>
            <FormControl>
                <InputLabel>Branch</InputLabel>
                <Input />
            </FormControl>
            <FormControl>
                <InputLabel>Email</InputLabel>
                <Input />
            </FormControl>
            <FormControl>
                <InputLabel>GPA</InputLabel>
                <Input />
            </FormControl>
            <FormControl>
                <InputLabel>phone</InputLabel>
                <Input />
            </FormControl>
            <Button>Add Student</Button>
        </FormGroup>
    )
}

export default AddUsers;
